description: It's another episode of veganized! That's where I take a viral recipe video and try to make it vegan. In today's video, I'm making tasty's buttermilk pancakes recipe vegan. Tasty 101 claims these are the fluffiest pancakes and the best pancakes ever. So I wanted to try to make fluffy vegan pancakes. With a few tweaks and recipe hacks, I think I made some pretty good vegan buttermilk pancakes. Disclaimer: This video description contains affiliate links. As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases
name: VEGANIZED! Tasty's Buttermilk Pancakes
